<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Bel-Aire</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1960, Bel-Aire has become a wealthy residential neighbourhood, seated
                overlooking North Glenmore Reservoir. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">An elite, exclusive community located in the southwest quadrant of Calgary, Alberta,
                Bel-Aire is bordered in the north by the Calgary Golf and Country Club, Elbow River and Glenmore
                Reservoir in the east, and Meadowlark Park community in the west.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">A smaller community, it is one of the wealthiest communities in Calgary, comprised of some of the most luxury Calgary homes, ideally located for its beautiful view
                of the city and reservoir.</p>

